meanings.definition: Suggested automatically by a computer program based on previous user input.
meanings.sent1: The autosuggested options made it easier to choose the right answer.
meanings.sent2: The autosuggested search results helped me find what I was looking for quickly.
meanings.sent3: The autosuggested movie recommendations were surprisingly accurate.
meanings.sent4: Her outfit was like an autosuggested ensemble, perfectly matching without any effort.
meanings.sent5: The autosuggested route on the map saved me a lot of time during my trip.
